 information on these limitations.
 
+Hyper-V enlightened VMCS
+~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+
+For Windows guests on Intel hosts, Hyper-V enlightened VMCS (eVMCS) can be
+enabled by setting the ``hw_hyperv_evmcs=true`` image property. Nova adds the
+``HW_CPU_X86_INTEL_VMX`` trait to the scheduler request, ensuring it selects
+only compatible Intel VMX compute hosts for builds and migrations.
+
 
 KVM performance tweaks
 ----------------------
